      <title>Envoy对我们说，乌克兰拥抱全停火的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-embraces-idea-of-full-ceasefire-envoy-to-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国的特使说，乌克兰无条件地支持与俄罗斯完全停火的想法，这超出了美国目前正在讨论的一个月能源基础设施休战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-embraces-idea-of-full-ceasefire-envoy-to-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦调查局，ATF形式工作队，研究特斯拉故意破坏浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/fbi-atf-form-task-force-to-investigate-wave-of-tesla-vandalism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦调查局已与酒精，烟草，枪支和炸药局成立了一个工作队，以协调对特斯拉公司的陈列室和充电站的越来越多的破坏和纵火事件进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/fbi-atf-form-task-force-to-investigate-wave-of-tesla-vandalism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格陵兰的硬线独立党离开了政府谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/greenland-s-hard-line-independence-party-leaves-government-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格陵兰的硬线独立党在本月的选举中排名第二，该党将在该领土上脱离丹麦的道路上的分歧之后，在新政府之外站在一个新政府之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/greenland-s-hard-line-independence-party-leaves-government-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
