    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔法院将丹尼尔·诺贝亚（Daniel Noboa）最终击败副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ecuador-court-hands-daniel-noboa-final-win-over-vice-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔的一名法院狭窄地证实了副总统维罗妮卡·阿巴德（Veronica Abad）的任期结束后，丹尼尔·诺贝亚（Daniel Noboa）总统是长期纠纷的赢家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ecuador-court-hands-daniel-noboa-final-win-over-vice-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 20:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局长德乔伊（Dejoy</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-postmaster-general-dejoy-steps-down-as-deputy-takes-reins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局长路易斯·德乔伊（Louis Dejoy）已辞职，加剧了他先前宣布的离开，因为该国邮政机构希望阻止财务损失并大修其业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/us-postmaster-general-dejoy-steps-down-as-deputy-takes-reins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 20:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的财政部长在销售几天后举行投资者的电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/turkey-s-simsek-to-hold-investor-call-after-days-of-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，土耳其财政部长穆罕默德·辛格克（Mehmet Simsek）将于周二与国际投资者举行电话，因为当局试图在被捕的主要反对派人物引发的湍流之后平息市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/turkey-s-simsek-to-hold-investor-call-after-days-of-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 20:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
